competitions.rules: Looks like the next challenge is Films! Pick your favorite movie song, turn it into a Mario Maker level by April 1. And if you want to pepper it with some trolls to celebrate the Day of Fools? Well, who are we to judge?

competition_group.name: Team Music Challenge
competition_group.rules:
The Team Music Challenge is our monthly level making challenge! Each month we will have a different theme for you to build a music level around. This could range from movies, TV shows, holidays, to a number of other themes.
Make sure to include #TeamMusic or #TM in either the level's title or description.
Anyone is able to submit a level for the Team Music Challenge. Just submit the level like normal and then add the Challenge tag with !addtags 000-000-000 Music Challenge, if the level shows up on this page, you're good to go.

competitions.rules: This months challenge is Musicals! Make a level based around your favorite musical by June 9.

teamSettings.AddLevelRequirements: Your level needs to be primarily a music level. That's it.
teamSettings.HaveFun: Have fun, remember to sing along if you know the lyrics to any song!
teamSettings.FrontPageDescription: Ever found it difficult to search for music levels from creators? Hopefully this place makes it easier to find and sort music levels by your tastes.
